{"tid":256225,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"小學老師麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2017-05-24T11:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T13:33:34.000Z","uid":96262,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7b53bbd05b7fe4307ab99316865f44d1fd8bc1","tid":256225,"uid":96262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係個啱啱考完dse既學生，膽粗粗返pt走去幫小學生對功課<br />\n初時都冇問題，但我發現小學生有啲問題好難教得明佢地，我想知日校老師會點教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 麻煩過兩招俾小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經教到頭都大埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 英文<br />\n我有個小二既細路英文長期唔識拼音同串字，讀就冇問題既。叫佢抄又抄過，拆字分開記又試過。但轉個頭又冇哂記憶。其實同佢默個範圍好短，3句短句only, 但係佢都記唔入腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想真心教佢學英文，唔係死背<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有試過教a e i o u啲讀音，好似Alan同Alen既分別咁，但佢都似乎get唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想知佢地最大難處係咩，同埋佢好唔專心應該用咩方法令佢專心啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 數學<br />\n又係小二既妹妹，睇磅去計個克同公斤都好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點做既步驟已經教左好多次 搵0-100有幾多細格再除開睇下一小格係幾多，然後再睇支針咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢成日都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 激死我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁多，多謝你睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我已經ot左幾日就係同班細路默書，每日又唔夠時間我驚埋佢個份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跪求方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf2978603d744fbeeef87584ee60e53cc01e504","tid":256225,"uid":96262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eddf13f0575b7718a54082ac86462002c59551c","tid":256225,"uid":17907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"數學我用除式教佢"},{"pid":"65fec7012777780960493351c3c935e3a1134959","tid":256225,"uid":96262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>數學我用除式教佢</blockquote><br />\n但佢乘數都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84674244c0a3bc42ad6c177f764ad240753c2b9","tid":256225,"uid":116159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"其實我都想問下Alan同Alen有乜分別...."},{"pid":"2e4606c567a2c59f0d4b2228a13ec04385031d4f","tid":256225,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都想問下Alan同Alen有乜分別....</blockquote><br />\nAlan alen lor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e76fa26e214bb06009cce0d04323f3d940a85e","tid":256225,"uid":54608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"英文我唔知啦，但係其實似乎佢對英文缺乏興趣咁喎，唔係嘅話chunking（即係將一個生字分幾段記）咁去記生字應該唔會記唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n數學嘅話，如果佢唔識除法，甚至乘法，<br />\n不如你test下佢其實記唔記得兩個一數，五個一數呢啲基本嘢啦，同埋識唔識連加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj